Notes: UMR leads by as many as 17; UMSL outscores the Lady Miners 29-5 to take a
53-46 lead before UMR posts a rally of its own.  UMR makes a 12-4 run to take
the lead for good on Jamie Forsberg's three-pointer with 2:47 to go.  Forsberg
makes 3-4 FTs down the stretch as UMR holds off the Riverwomen to win.
Game.Officials: Phil Griffin,  Randy Dillon,  Ray Taylor
